    {
      "id": "pat-01",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🧭 The Question",
      "position": {
        "x": 831.6666666666666,
        "y": -445
      },
      "width": 320,
      "height": 200,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "Do we have something **patentable** — not just interesting, useful, or clever — but defensible as a *system*?",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
