    {
      "id": "pat-02",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "❌ Not Patentable (Alone)",
      "position": {
        "x": 395,
        "y": -85
      },
      "width": 340,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "- Node graphs\n- Auto-layout\n- AI coding tools\n- Agents\n- RAG\n- Orchestration\n\nAll are **prior art** when taken individually.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
