    {
      "id": "pat-03",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "✅ Potentially Patentable Core",
      "position": {
        "x": 855,
        "y": -85
      },
      "width": 380,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "**System-level combination:**\n\n• Graph is the *primary persistent artifact*\n• Graph may be authored **headlessly** (no layout)\n• Rendering is a **derived projection**, not state\n• AI mutates graph structure, not pixels\n• Copy/paste transmits executable graph state\n• Stable IDs + history preserved across views\n• Offline (Codex) and online (agents/RAG) share the same graph",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
