    {
      "id": "pat-05",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🏗️ Competitive Context",
      "position": {
        "x": 20,
        "y": 385
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "Big players (e.g. Google Antigravity):\n\n• UI-first\n• SaaS-hosted\n• Execution-centric\n• Rendering assumed\n• Ephemeral cognition\n\nTwilite is orthogonal, not replaceable.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
