    {
      "id": "pat-06",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "📌 Current Status",
      "position": {
        "x": 980,
        "y": 405
      },
      "width": 320,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "• Architecture is real\n• Insight recently crystallized\n• Patentability depends on **mechanism**, not philosophy\n• Needs concrete system description\n• Not ready to file — ready to *define*",
