      "id": "pat-07",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🛤️ Next Decision Fork",
      "position": {
        "x": 960,
        "y": 805
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "Options:\n\n1. Draft plain-English system claim\n2. Identify prior art to distinguish\n3. Consult patent attorney (after #1)\n4. Decide *not* to patent (and why)\n\nNo urgency — clarity first.",
